com.rli.vds.util

Interface UserDefinedEntry2


  • public interface UserDefinedEntry2
    The interface to implements custom objects operations (new style) like select, insert, update, delete and authenticate The operations must be implemented in the corresponding functions. The 'Properties' object in each function contains all the Meta information properties like Connection String, Filter, Attributes, etc. it is used also as an output structure to hold the result of the interception (that may include modified input parameters)
